<p class="courseblockdesc">
Analytical and numerical treatment of linear, discrete systems. Nonlinear discrete systems. Course Information: 3 undergraduate hours. 4 graduate hours. Prerequisite(s): CME 200 or the equivalent and <a href="/search/?P=MATH%20220" title="MATH&#160;220" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'MATH 220');">MATH&#160;220</a>.<br />
